        <mxCell id="8LrE9ll0woaESgyi9E8p-39" value="&lt;pre style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;Роутеры провайдера PE используют последовательные порты (Serial) &lt;br/&gt;для всех подключений.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 21px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-family: Helvetica; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;IP-адресация:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-family: Helvetica; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;- Сеть провайдера (между PE):&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;    172.16.0.0/30 (PE1-PE2)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;    172.16.1.0/30 (PE2-PE3)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 21px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-family: Helvetica; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; 172.16.2.0/30 (PE1-PE3)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-family: Helvetica; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;- Подключения клиентов:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-family: Helvetica; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; R1 - PE1: 10.1.1.0/30 (R1: .2, PE1: .1)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-family: Helvetica; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; R2 - PE2: 10.2.2.0/30 (R2: .2, PE2: .1)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-family: Helvetica; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; R3 - PE3: 10.3.3.0/30 (R3: .2, PE3: .1)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-family: Helvetica; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;- Локальные сети филиалов:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-family: Helvetica; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; Филиал A: 192.168.1.0/24 (шлюз R1 Fa0/0: 192.168.1.1)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-family: Helvetica; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; Филиал B: 192.168.2.0/24 (шлюз R2 Fa0/0: 192.168.2.1)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-family: Helvetica; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; Филиал C: 192.168.3.0/24 (шлюз R3 Fa0/0: 192.168.3.1)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-family: Helvetica; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;- Loopback интерфейсы на маршрутизаторах провайдера для идентификации:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-family: Helvetica; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; PE1: Lo0 = 1.1.1.1/32&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-family: Helvetica; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; PE2: Lo0 = 2.2.2.2/32&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-family: Helvetica; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; PE3: Lo0 = 3.3.3.3/32&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;" vertex="1" parent="1">
